\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {5.1}{\ignorespaces Pipeline ablation at a glance for the shipped \texttt  {robust8-nr} cascade (filter-then-route composition). (a) Drone-positive paired surfaces: the always-routing router adds a small per-modality lift and the per-frame filter finishes it (Svanstr\"om $0.742\to 0.946$); Anti-UAV confirms no-harm. Whiskers are 95\% bootstrap confidence intervals (the central range of the metric over $1{,}000$ resamples of the frames; bars whose whiskers do not overlap differ by more than sampling noise). (b) Confuser surfaces: bare $\to $ patch $\to $ \texttt  {mlp\_v5\_v4} $\to $ router $\to $ composed frame fire rates. The no-reject router never vetoes a confuser frame, so its router-only bar stays at the bare rate and the per-frame filter owns suppression: RGB $30.4\% \to 1.4\%$ composed, thermal $29.4\% \to 2.8\%$. Generated from \texttt  {results\_noreject/tier1\_results.json} by \texttt  {thesis\_eval/gen\_ablation\_figure.py}.}}{54}{figure.caption.48}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:pipeline_ablation}{{5.1}{54}{Pipeline ablation at a glance for the shipped \texttt {robust8-nr} cascade (filter-then-route composition). (a) Drone-positive paired surfaces: the always-routing router adds a small per-modality lift and the per-frame filter finishes it (Svanstr\"om $0.742\to 0.946$); Anti-UAV confirms no-harm. Whiskers are 95\% bootstrap confidence intervals (the central range of the metric over $1{,}000$ resamples of the frames; bars whose whiskers do not overlap differ by more than sampling noise). (b) Confuser surfaces: bare $\to $ patch $\to $ \texttt {mlp\_v5\_v4} $\to $ router $\to $ composed frame fire rates. The no-reject router never vetoes a confuser frame, so its router-only bar stays at the bare rate and the per-frame filter owns suppression: RGB $30.4\% \to 1.4\%$ composed, thermal $29.4\% \to 2.8\%$. Generated from \texttt {results\_noreject/tier1\_results.json} by \texttt {thesis\_eval/gen\_ablation\_figure.py}}{figure.caption.48}{}}
